Package: scschooldata
Title: Fetch and Process South Carolina School Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Al", "Martin", email = "almartin@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Al Martin [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Al Martin <almartin@example.com>
Description: Downloads and processes school data from the South Carolina
    Department of Education (SCDE). Provides functions for fetching enrollment
    data from Active Student Headcounts and SC Report Cards, transforming it
    into tidy format for analysis. Supports data from 2018-present via
    SC Report Cards and 2013-present via Active Student Headcounts.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
